# AI Workflow Log

> Audit trail for AI-assisted development sessions. Agents write to this file
> as events occur. Humans read it for audit, calibration, and retrospectives.
>
> Format: `[YYYY-MM-DDThh:mmZ] [event_type] [mode] [detail]`
> See references/06-evals-and-tracing.md for the full event taxonomy.

---

## Session Log

> Each session appends entries below. Do not delete old entries.

```
[YYYY-MM-DDThh:mmZ] session_start [mode] agent=[agent-name] contract_version=[N] memory=[engram|native|manual]
[YYYY-MM-DDThh:mmZ] contract_load [mode] CLAUDE.md contract_version=[N] baseline_warnings=[N]
[YYYY-MM-DDThh:mmZ] memory_retrieval [mode] source=[engram|native|handover] retrieved=[what]
...
[YYYY-MM-DDThh:mmZ] session_close [mode] mem_summary=[saved|failed] handover=[updated|created|skipped]
```

---

## Architectural Decision Log

> Significant decisions that affect the project long-term. More detail than
> the session log format above.

### [YYYY-MM-DD] — [Decision title]

**Context:** [why this decision was needed]
**Decision:** [what was decided]
**Evidence:** [file:line or test result that informed the decision]
**Alternatives rejected:** [what was not chosen and why]
**Mode:** [light / standard / strict]

